data.description: Step inside to discover the heart of this home--a spacious and thoughtfully designed floor plan adorned with high vaulted ceilings, open concept common space, and a cozy wood stove. The kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring a stylish breakfast bar where you can savor your morning coffee while planning your next Alaskan adventure.Stainless steel appliances, ample storage, and a well-appointed layout make this kitchen a chef's delight. The counter tops are scheduled to be replaced soon and will add even more style and value. The master large suite includes a double vanity complete with modern fixtures and a walk-in closet. The additional three bedrooms provide versatility and comfort for your family and guests. There is also a fifth bonus room you can use as an office, gym, hobby room, or for other purposes. And the garage is oversized with three stalls and plenty of space for ample storage space to accommodate tools, equipment, and outdoor gear with ease. Venture outside to the generous yard, where endless possibilities await. Located just moments away from Ft. Wainwright's back gate, this property offers easy access to the base and nearby amenities, ensuring a convenient and seamless lifestyle. Don't miss your chance to make this house your home. Welcome home!
